{"tid":1647321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片]呢個警察好過份","createTime":"2019-10-11T16:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T17:02:19.000Z","uid":149188,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2fd704cb8e0ecb6f122c48b1351e9ffc0f22ca7d","tid":1647321,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:46:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家自己睇佢做左乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">去片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1773510267/posts/10206109527455211?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1773510267%2Fposts%2F10206109527455211%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=11292928\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1773510267/posts/10206109527455211?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JwNTnXz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJwNTnXz.png&h=562b7bcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過去3個月唔同黑警做左啲寫list都長到列唔曬佢衰嘢 我真係以為好警察死淨離島區守水塘果啲 但原來仲有呢啲警察 其實有時你入到區放曬tg 開曬槍咁冇人會服你 比你升到職又點 一陣政府玩夠要清算你地咪受靶 (其實雨傘果陣試過) 點解唔落區嘅時候溝通多啲 大家好嚟好去咪算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n70年代未有老廉果陣 警察自己都有宣傳片教你地點同人溝通啦 <br />\n<img src=\"https://www.facebook.com/1233376897/posts/10214790711541383?sfns=mo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1233376897%2Fposts%2F10214790711541383%3Fsfns%3Dmo&h=b18be258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1233376897/posts/10214790711541383?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1233376897%2Fposts%2F10214790711541383%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=913aaf19\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1233376897/posts/10214790711541383?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tCLURPP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtCLURPP.png&h=7db2122f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nwnTnWv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnwnTnWv.png&h=12c48d68&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6MXPBw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6MXPBw.png&h=f9d7200d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T8eB49R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT8eB49R.png&h=81a2dd44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後mon po狗睇到呢到就同你啲手足講下 小心被清算<br />\n大家都係香港人 你收得人工就要揸槍 但你枝槍射去邊得你先決定到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"242d311be9e5ed6a2da7f783bb14733c0f2f3f73","tid":1647321,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:47:18.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"573351d67a5efbcac27ef5cf76543b45f2a6aad7","tid":1647321,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:47:31.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"af81574e6698965f9bc7cdd5f782078fe3ec5832","tid":1647321,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:47:51.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"0d25b03e1704d44847caec354e2cf3c627252270","tid":1647321,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:48:03.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"32554f6393b0fe158c9134e46c3e5a20370ba45b","tid":1647321,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:48:13.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"dd8b1acc6bcd4a2c85fc9bf4593468076a9e0048","tid":1647321,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:48:28.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"0cccf8f00cfbaae076702260376a7c220145b62d","tid":1647321,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:48:41